{"lastModified":1764336966859,"uri":"c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: West Mediterranean - Naples/Sicily, Riviera/Corsica/Sardinia\nWinter Operating Area: Leeward Islands, Windwards Islands, U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands\n\nHALCYON is a 24.38m / 80ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2024 by Sunreef Yachts. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 4. The guest cabins comprise of four queen cabins.","blueprint":{"name":"HALCYON","images":["/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::d71e88a0-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::d7205d60-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::e1fde3b0-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::e675fe50-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::ddf294a0-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::ec408990-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::ec401460-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::eff09940-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::f723b530-a97e-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::f726