neeboard","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear","quantity":"8"},{"label":"Tube","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Kayaks (2 Pax)","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Floating Mats","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Swim Platform","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Boarding Ladder","quantity":"2"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Underwater Video","quantity":""},{"label":"Sea Bobs","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Sea Scooters","quantity":""}],"entertainment":["Salon TV","Wi-Fi"],"tenders":["Dinghy 80 hp"]},"crew":[{"name":"Adrien Rolland","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::241370c0-b0bf-11ee-ae6e-e783bbc597f3.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Captain Adrien is a seasoned seafarer with a lifelong passion for the ocean. Starting as a young sailor aboard the family boat, he honed his skills and knowledge over the years. With an RYA Yachtmaster Offshore certification and a degree in nautical marketing engineering, Adrien is a skilled captain known for his meticulous boat maintenance and repair abilities.\n\nHaving navigated the waters of the Mediterranean, Caribbean, Atlantic, Indian and Brittany, Adrien ensures the safety and comfort of his passengers and crew in all conditions. His patient and approachable demeanor, coupled with his dedication to boat care, make him a trusted leader.\n\nCombining French art de vivre with British nautical tradition, Adrien brings a unique perspective to every voyage aboard Halcyon. Cruising with Captain Adrien guarantees an unforgettable experience filled with lasting memories.\n"},{"name":"Christina Merianos","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::f0229800-a979-11ee-ba50-039c28b06e4d::assets::47eef9b0-b0bf-11ee-ae6e-e783bbc597f3.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Chef","bio":"Chef Christina is a Midwest Cincinnati native, and after moving to Manhattan and working 15 years in the fashion world she decided to go back to her favorite job of all time, restaurants... Growing up in a Greek household, food and cooking was always a huge part of her life.  Christina comes from a long line of a family with culinary careers so there is no surprise she ended up being a Yacht Chef.  She also loves being at Sea and has been boating her entire life. After working many years in NYC restaurants, she moved to LA to be a private chef, then took a chance on a job that would combine two of her favorite activities cooking and the sea and has been happily hosting and cooking aboard yachts the last 3 years.  She is outgoing, happy, funny, and looks forward to helping make your trip one of the best memories of your life!    "}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":6800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":6800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":10000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":10000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer: Mediterranean -  High Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-06-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-09-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"note":"https://www.cyabrochure.com/eb/2903/phydX/8947/4/9/1/#:~:text=Additional%20Rate%20Details,total%20charter%20fee.","currency":"EUR","inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","subTotal":8750000,"totalTax":1540000,"total":10290000,"lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded","quantity":1,"unitPrice":7000000,"amount":7000000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.22}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.25,"unitPrice":7000000,"amount":1750000}],"charterFee":7000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Naples","type":"Custom Area","category":["Naples"],"coordinates":[14.5625,40.9125],"bbox":[14.025,40.683333,15.1,41.141667]},{"label":"Sicily","type":"Geo subunit","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Sicily"],"coordinates":[14.155397130095018,37.59291213666052],"bbox":[12.435546875,